<div id="review_551805415" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/551805415" />
    <a title="Rajat Ubhaykar" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4686064-rajat-ubhaykar"><img alt="Rajat Ubhaykar" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1352663955p2/4686064.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/551805415?book_show_action=true">Mar 19, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Rajat Ubhaykar" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Rajat Ubhaykar" href="/user/show/4686064-rajat-ubhaykar">Rajat Ubhaykar</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4686064-rajat-ubhaykar?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4686064-rajat-ubhaykar?shelf=journalism">journalism</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4686064-rajat-ubhaykar?shelf=history">history</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4686064-rajat-ubhaykar?shelf=must-read-at-least-once">must-read-at-least-once</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4686064-rajat-ubhaykar?shelf=nook">nook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4686064-rajat-ubhaykar?shelf=africa">africa</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4686064-rajat-ubhaykar?shelf=travel">travel</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/4686064-rajat-ubhaykar?shelf=post-colonial">post-colonial</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer551805415" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6962688311704821687">This book came as a revelation to me! It enlightened me about the history, spirit and psyche of Africa (a meaningless appellation), and made me acutely aware of my smug ignorance about this vast, endlessly diverse continent. Kapuscinski, who’s covered dozens of coups and revolutions as a conflict reporter in the era of decolonization, writes about the continent and its people with empathy, never exoticizing it. I would go as far as to say that The Shadow of the Sun is probably the best work of t</span>
  <span id="freeText6962688311704821687" style="display:none">This book came as a revelation to me! It enlightened me about the history, spirit and psyche of Africa (a meaningless appellation), and made me acutely aware of my smug ignorance about this vast, endlessly diverse continent. Kapuscinski, who’s covered dozens of coups and revolutions as a conflict reporter in the era of decolonization, writes about the continent and its people with empathy, never exoticizing it. I would go as far as to say that The Shadow of the Sun is probably the best work of travel writing I’ve read. Highly recommended!</span>
  <a data-text-id="6962688311704821687" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


